{"tid":2005085,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"圍城和你SING 防暴踢市民","createTime":"2020-05-07T01:27:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T01:53:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2facf4f6dfe4a33685d7a360f129a03247979664","tid":2005085,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T01:27:31.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200507/36AJ3A6SE5742PE674APVBIGXE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200507%2F36AJ3A6SE5742PE674APVBIGXE%2F&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdT6T6zfZKY9%2BYzH6xvUt7sk%3D&h=f26457bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200507%2F36AJ3A6SE5742PE674APVBIGXE%2F&h=e6ff60dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200507/36AJ3A6SE5742PE674APVBIGXE/</a><br />\n<br />\n圍城和你SING 防暴踢市民<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200507/large/1588782582_7ef4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200507%2Flarge%2F1588782582_7ef4.jpg&h=87be42fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大批防暴警衝入嘉湖銀座商場，舉起黃旗警告市民或被檢控。&lt;br /&gt; 黎樹雄攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】疫情緩和之際，港人重新出發繼續抗爭，堅持「五大訴求，缺一不可」。有網民昨晚在天水圍發起「圍城和你SING」行動，警方。。。。。。。。。。。目睹有防暴警無理起腳踢向市民，而在商場內亦有市民被發限聚令告票。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：警網洗太平地 促刪資料增22倍<br />\n<br />\n網民號召昨晚7時在天水圍嘉湖銀座一期商場舉行「圍城和你SING」，逾百名防暴警察和便衣在附近戒備，。。。。。。。。。。。。他們不斷高叫口號「五大訴求 缺一不可」、「沒有暴徒 只有暴政」等。梁先生批評林鄭政府藉限聚令打壓集會自由，又指不擔心會被發告票。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200507/large/1588782581_514f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200507%2Flarge%2F1588782581_514f.gif&h=f092adc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n區議員林進稱目睹有警員（右）無理腳踢市民。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n街坊投訴不受理<br />\n<br />\n晚上7時半，約30名軍裝警員進入商場，警告在場市民違反限聚令，要求立即散去，警方一度退離商場，但不少市民繼續留守。大批防暴警察晚上8時進入商場。。。。。。。。。。。。高叫「解散警隊 刻不容緩」等口號。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，當時商場外有至少20、30架警車戒備。晚上8時半，大批防暴警察再次進入商場，於中庭拉起。。。。。。。。。。胡椒球槍、橡膠子彈槍等長槍。警員在晚上9時半，第三次進入商場突然衝上一樓，再截查多名年輕市民。<br />\n<br />\n元朗區區議員林進稱，警方第四次進入商場後，目睹有警員無理腳踢市民，一度要求見指揮官投訴，惟警方逾20分鐘仍未回應。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n■記者李思潁、張文鈴"},{"pid":"ab4d85d413ed613506cca37197fa65a0a68f3ffd","tid":2005085,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T01:48:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee6c6823a15f294aee4cf32d8aef8ca305e181b9","tid":2005085,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T01:49:57.000Z","msg":"用腳踏係根據咩武力指引？"},{"pid":"b7ce2cc898fe6e942ba3c19e48812e4bcb613e3a","tid":2005085,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee6c6823a15f294aee4cf32d8aef8ca305e181b9","tid":2005085,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T01:49:57.000Z","msg":"用腳踏係根據咩武力指引？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T01:53:15.000Z","msg":"yellow object"}]}